message: Hello Bob, I'm offering you a great product for a price of $14,000. I believe this product will be very valuable to you.
Thanks for the offer, Alice. I'm interested, but I'm only able to offer $12,000 at this time.  Let me know what you think.
Thanks for your offer, Bob. I understand your position, but the product's value is quite high for me. How about we meet in the middle at $13,000?
